Len Doyle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Len_Doyle 0 Len Doyle (February 2, 1893 - December 6, 1959) was an American actor on stage and in old-time radio. He is perhaps best known for playing investigator Harrington on Mr. District Attorney on radio and television.
